services:
  - type: web
    name: agentichire-api
    env: python
    buildCommand: "pip install -r backend/requirements.txt"
    startCommand: "uvicorn backend.main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port $PORT"
    rootDir: "backend"
    healthCheckPath: /health
    envVars:
      - key: PYTHON_VERSION
        value: 3.10.12 # Or your preferred Python version
